data.name: Season 2
data.overview: Season two is shaped by Offreds pregnancy and her ongoing fight to free her future child from the dystopian horrors of Gilead. Gilead is within you is a favorite saying of Aunt Lydia and in this season, Offred and all our characters will fight against  or succumb to  this dark truth.
